                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 11513/2.</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                Minister <persName type="to">Bryan</persName></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-02-04"><hi rend="italic">February 4,
                                1908</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Root informs Mr. Bryan that he will represent the President as
                            special ambassador at the funeral.)</p>
